It's convenient in case of a visit.
'However it is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on the back you should lay hands comfortably with the elbows slightly bent. Helena Prokopova, President of the Association of Bourreliers-matresses and decorators who for several years has devoted himself to the problem of a healthy sleep and the ergonomics of furniture and teaches it in specialized schools.
For a two-seater bed each needs its own bed base and mattress, so be careful, however, during the shop to choose the height of the mattress.
