This paved the way for an agreement on Wednesday to eliminate the rest of the matter of about 500 pounds, according to one official who referred to the condition of anonymity because of the sensitivity of the issue.
The agreement seems to be one of the most important outcomes of the 47-nation Nuclear Security Summit, organized on the initiative of Obama; where Belarus was excluded.
