Alexandre Guérini has been indicted for abuse of social goods, misappropriation of public funds and property, concealment, active corruption, trafficking in influence and possession of ammunition, says his lawyer.
"Alexandre Guérini is combative and wants to explain himself on all the questions the magistrate is going to ask him, not fantasies."
"It is easy to prosecute him for a multitude of reprehensible counts, it is something else to prove them," said his lawyer, Florence Rault, to the AFP before the hearing of his client.
